cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use this archive, cite this Part III release and also cite the CDFD Runtime DOI when using runtime-linked CDFL diagnostics."
title: "CDFD Part III: Adaptive Flux Limitation Biology and Medicine - Constraint-Driven Flux Dynamics"
version: "1.0.0"
