abstract: "Public Part III biology-and-medicine archive for the Constraint-Driven Flux Dynamics project, including a seventeen-paper manuscript spine, supplementary scripts, generated model diagnostics, bibliography, claim-status notes, named biology laws/tests, and reproducibility instructions. The archive translates CDFL and Adaptive Flux Limitation into clinical systems language while keeping runtime diagnostics separate from empirical clinical validation."
